Voyager Alembic migrations.

Usage (from packages/db/):
    export DATABASE_URL="postgresql+psycopg://voyageradmin:<pwd>@psql-voyager-sexwh5.postgres.database.azure.com:5432/voyager?sslmode=require"
    uv run alembic upgrade head

The first revision (0001_initial_schema.py) creates all five tables:
videos, transcripts, comments, insights, briefs.
